202988064.Title: Premier 20 in. 2.42 cu. ft. Electric Range in White
202988064.Description: The Premier 20 in. Freestanding Electric Range puts all the features and convenience of a full-size range into a unit that will accommodate even the most intimate of kitchen spaces. All Premier ranges come with an Exclusive Lifetime Warranty on all Top Burner Elements - Your assurance that you are purchasing a top quality product. Equipped with a lift-up cook top and support rod, this range is a cinch to keep clean. Safety features like the Surface Indicator Light, will let you know at a glance if cooktop burners are on. Our "Keep Warm" Thermostat enables you to set your range to 150°, keeping your food warm without continuing to cook until ready to eat and the Fully Insulated Oven comes with 2 Heavy-Duty Oven Racks with 4 Adjustable Positions. Color: White.

309297432.Title: PREMIUM 20 in. 2.2 cu. ft. Electric Range in White
309297432.Description: PREMIUM's 20 in. 2.2 cu. ft. Electric Range in White is the perfect appliance for your apartment, condo or office kitchen. Just as in larger units there is an in-door window and oven light to allow users to check on food while it is cooking, 2 adjustable wire racks, a broiler tray and grid included, and a handy removable storage drawer. With its small footprint, it conserves space while providing all the functionality you need to cook healthy meals at home.

301398974.Title: Avanti 20 in. 2.1 cu. ft. Electric Range in White
301398974.Description: This Avanti 20 in. Electric Range Comes with a Backsplash and Storage Drawer. It features 4 coil burners, 2.1 cu. ft. capacity, deluxe see-thru glass oven door, oven cavity light, a backsplash and leveling legs. Fits great in small areas where most regular size stoves wont. Color: White.

309052082.Title: Frigidaire 24 in. 1.9 cu. ft. Freestanding Electric Range with Manual Clean in White
309052082.Description: This 24 in. electric range is compact in design, but not in capacity - oven can easily fit a 10 lb. turkey. Convenient storage drawer offers extra space to store your cookware. Keeping the bottom of your oven clean is easier with a hidden heating element. The stylish knobs are color-coordinated to match the finish of the range. ADA Compliant. Color: White.
